review_data.content: Purchased a sandwich and a cake today and was short changed. Maybe they can't count and it was a mistake but check your change if you go here. I wont be going again.

review_data.title: Breakfast
review_data.content: During our stay in Zurich we had breakfast from here both mornings. The display of products in the bakery all look incredible. We had croissants and pan au chocolat and I don't think I've had better... it was like a melted Kinder egg inside!
